## Tokens — single source of truth

| Token | File |
|---|---|
| ColorScheme (light + dark) | `app/src/main/java/{{PACKAGE_PATH}}/ui/theme/Color.kt` |
| Typography | `app/src/main/java/{{PACKAGE_PATH}}/ui/theme/Type.kt` |
| Shapes | `app/src/main/java/{{PACKAGE_PATH}}/ui/theme/Shape.kt` |
| Spacing (custom) | `app/src/main/java/{{PACKAGE_PATH}}/ui/theme/Spacing.kt` |
| Theme wrapper | `app/src/main/java/{{PACKAGE_PATH}}/ui/theme/Theme.kt` |
| Motion | Material 3 `MotionTokens` (no custom file — use the M3 tokens directly) |

**NEVER use values outside these tokens.** No `Modifier.padding(13.dp)`, no inline `Color(0xFF3A4F6B)`, no inline `TextStyle(fontSize = 13.sp)`, no one-off `RoundedCornerShape(7.dp)`.

